<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>장바구니 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --bg-soft: #ece8e1;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #111111;
      --text: #1f1f1f;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      --radius-xl: 30px;
      --max: 1280px;
      --green: #1f7a45;
      --green-bg: #edf7f0;
      --red: #b23a2c;
      --red-bg: #fff1ee;
      --orange: #b76a1d;
      --orange-bg: #fff4e8;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    img { display: block; width: 100%; }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--black);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(245, 243, 239, 0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .header-inner {
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .page { padding: 44px 0 80px; }

    .page-head { margin-bottom: 28px; }

    .page-head small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .page-head h1 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .page-head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .warn-global {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: var(--red-bg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(178, 58, 44, 0.18);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cart-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 26px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cart-card { padding: 26px; }

    .summary-card {
      padding: 24px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 110px;
    }

    .cart-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .cart-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .cart-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .thumb {
      width: 110px;
      height: 138px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--bg-soft);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .thumb img {
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .thumb-empty {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      background: var(--bg-soft);
    }

    .item-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .item-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .remove-form button {
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      color: #8b8680;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .item-meta {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .item-meta-line {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .add-on-meta {
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .add-on-meta strong {
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .price-line {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .item-price {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .item-subtotal {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .status-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 32px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .badge-ok {
      background: var(--green-bg);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .badge-soldout {
      background: var(--red-bg);
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .badge-warning {
      background: var(--orange-bg);
      color: var(--orange);
    }

    .stock-note {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .stock-note.ok {
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .stock-note.warning {
      background: var(--orange-bg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(183, 106, 29, 0.16);
      color: var(--orange);
    }

    .stock-note.soldout {
      background: var(--red-bg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(178, 58, 44, 0.18);
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .qty-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .qty-inline {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px;
    }

    .qty-inline form { margin: 0; }

    .qty-btn {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--black);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .qty-update-form {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .qty-input {
      width: 72px;
      height: 38px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
    }

    .qty-save {
      height: 38px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .summary-box {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .summary-total {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--black);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .summary-note {
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .summary-note.warning {
      background: var(--red-bg);
      border-color: rgba(178, 58, 44, 0.18);
      color: var(--red);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .summary-actions {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      height: 54px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .btn-disabled {
      background: #d9d2c8;
      color: #7e7569;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .empty-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 50px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .empty-card h2 {
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .empty-card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .empty-actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .cart-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .summary-card { position: static; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { padding: 0 16px; }
      .header-actions { display: none; }

      .cart-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

      .thumb {
        width: 100%;
        height: 280px;
      }

      .cart-card,
      .summary-card,
      .empty-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%
    const hasStockIssue = (cart || []).some(item => {
      const stock = Number(item.stock || 0);
      const qty = Number(item.quantity || 0);
      const soldout = item.productStatus === 'soldout' || stock <= 0;
      return soldout || qty > stock;
    });

    const totalItemCount = (cart || []).reduce((sum, item) => sum + Number(item.quantity || 0), 0);

    const productOnlyTotal = (cart || []).reduce((sum, item) => {
      return sum + (Number(item.price || 0) * Number(item.quantity || 0));
    }, 0);

    const addOnGrandTotal = (cart || []).reduce((sum, item) => {
      return sum + Number(item.addOnTotal || 0);
    }, 0);
  %>

  <div class="topbar">DAMORE OFFICIAL ONLINE STORE</div>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-logo">DAMORE</span>
          <span class="brand-sub">the more, the mood</span>
        </a>

        <div class="header-actions">
          <% if (typeof currentUser !== 'undefined' && currentUser) { %>
            <a href="/my-orders">내 주문내역</a>
            <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/order/lookup">주문조회</a>
            <a href="/auth">로그인 / 회원가입</a>
          <% } %>
          <a href="/cart">장바구니 <%= cartCount %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-head">
        <small>Shopping Cart</small>
        <h1>장바구니</h1>
        <p>담아둔 상품을 확인하고 수량을 조정한 뒤 주문을 진행하세요.</p>
      </div>

      <% if (!cart || cart.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="empty-card">
          <h2>장바구니가 비어 있습니다</h2>
          <p>마음에 드는 상품을 담아보세요. 담은 상품은 여기서 한눈에 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>

          <div class="empty-actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-dark" style="max-width: 220px;">상품 보러가기</a>
            <a href="/order/lookup" class="btn btn-light" style="max-width: 220px;">비회원 주문조회</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <% if (hasStockIssue) { %>
          <div class="warn-global">
            현재 장바구니에 재고 문제가 있는 상품이 있습니다.
            품절 상품을 삭제하거나 수량을 재고 이하로 조정해야 주문할 수 있습니다.
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="cart-wrap">
          <div class="card cart-card">
            <div class="cart-list">
              <% cart.forEach(item => { %>
                <%
                  const stock = Number(item.stock || 0);
                  const qty = Number(item.quantity || 0);
                  const isSoldout = item.productStatus === 'soldout' || stock <= 0;
                  const isOverStock = !isSoldout && qty > stock;
                  const addOnNames = Array.isArray(item.addOnNames) ? item.addOnNames : [];
                  const addOnIds = Array.isArray(item.addOnIds) ? item.addOnIds : [];
                  const addOnTotal = Number(item.addOnTotal || 0);
                  const lineSubtotal = (Number(item.price || 0) * qty) + addOnTotal;
                %>

                <div class="cart-item">
                  <div class="thumb">
                    <% if (item.image) { %>
                      <img src="<%= item.image %>" alt="<%= item.name %>" />
                    <% } else { %>
                      <div class="thumb-empty">이미지 없음</div>
                    <% } %>
                  </div>

                  <div>
                    <div class="item-top">
                      <div class="item-name"><%= item.name %></div>

                      <form method="POST" action="/cart/remove" class="remove-form">
                        <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="option" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= addOnIds.join(',') %>" />
                        <button type="submit">삭제</button>
                      </form>
                    </div>

                    <div class="item-meta">
                      <div class="item-meta-line">
                        <% if (item.option) { %>
                          옵션: <%= item.option %>
                        <% } else { %>
                          기본 옵션
                        <% } %>
                      </div>

                      <% if (item.color) { %>
                        <div class="item-meta-line">컬러: <%= item.color %></div>
                      <% } %>

                      <% if (addOnNames.length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="add-on-meta">
                          <strong>추가상품</strong><br />
                          <%= addOnNames.join(', ') %>
                          <% if (addOnTotal > 0) { %>
                            <br />추가금액: <strong><%= addOnTotal.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
                          <% } %>
                        </div>
                      <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <div class="status-row">
                      <% if (isSoldout) { %>
                        <span class="badge badge-soldout">품절</span>
                      <% } else if (isOverStock) { %>
                        <span class="badge badge-warning">재고 부족</span>
                      <% } else { %>
                        <span class="badge badge-ok">구매 가능</span>
                      <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <% if (isSoldout) { %>
                      <div class="stock-note soldout">
                        이 상품은 현재 품절입니다. 장바구니에서 삭제 후 진행해주세요.
                      </div>
                    <% } else if (isOverStock) { %>
                      <div class="stock-note warning">
                        현재 수량 <strong><%= qty %>개</strong> / 재고 <strong><%= stock %>개</strong><br />
                        주문하려면 수량을 재고 이하로 줄여야 합니다.
                      </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                      <div class="stock-note ok">
                        현재 주문 가능 재고: <strong><%= stock %>개</strong>
                      </div>
                    <% } %>

                    <div class="price-line">
                      <span class="item-price"><%= Number(item.price).toLocaleString() %>원</span>
                      <span class="item-subtotal">
                        소계 <strong><%= lineSubtotal.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
                      </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="qty-wrap">
                      <div class="qty-inline">
                        <form method="POST" action="/cart/decrease">
                          <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="option" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= addOnIds.join(',') %>" />
                          <button type="submit" class="qty-btn">-</button>
                        </form>

                        <span style="min-width: 24px; text-align:center; font-weight:700;"><%= item.quantity %></span>

                        <form method="POST" action="/cart/increase">
                          <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="option" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>" />
                          <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= addOnIds.join(',') %>" />
                          <button type="submit" class="qty-btn">+</button>
                        </form>
                      </div>

                      <form method="POST" action="/cart/update" class="qty-update-form">
                        <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="option" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= addOnIds.join(',') %>" />
                        <input type="number" name="quantity" min="1" value="<%= item.quantity %>" class="qty-input" required />
                        <button type="submit" class="qty-save">변경</button>
                      </form>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card summary-card">
            <h2 class="summary-title">주문 요약</h2>

            <div class="summary-box">
              <div class="summary-row">
                <span>상품 수</span>
                <strong><%= totalItemCount %>개</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="summary-row">
                <span>상품 합계</span>
                <strong><%= Number(productOnlyTotal).toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="summary-row">
                <span>추가상품 합계</span>
                <strong><%= Number(addOnGrandTotal).toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="summary-row">
                <span>배송비</span>
                <strong>0원</strong>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-total">
              <span>총 결제금액</span>
              <span><%= Number(totalPrice).toLocaleString() %>원</span>
            </div>

            <% if (hasStockIssue) { %>
              <div class="summary-note warning">
                재고 문제로 현재 주문 진행이 불가합니다.<br />
                품절 상품 삭제 또는 수량 조정 후 다시 시도해주세요.
              </div>
            <% } else { %>
              <div class="summary-note">
                장바구니 상품은 수량 변경 후 즉시 반영됩니다. 비회원도 그대로 주문 진행이 가능합니다.
              </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="summary-actions">
              <% if (hasStockIssue) { %>
                <div class="btn btn-disabled">재고 문제 해결 후 주문 가능</div>
              <% } else { %>
                <a href="/order" class="btn btn-dark">주문하기</a>
              <% } %>
              <a href="/" class="btn btn-light">계속 쇼핑하기</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>